import React, { useState } from 'react'; const Contact=()=>{ const [item,setitem]=useState({ fullname:'', email:'', mobile:'', Comment:'' }); const inputval=(event)=>{ const {name,value}=event.target; setitem((oldval)=>{ return{ ...oldval, [name]:value, } }) } const submitval=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); setitem(''); alert(item.fullname) } return(<>

Contact Us

) } export default Contact;
